      <Text fill="WHITE" fontSmoothingType="LCD" layoutX="472.0" layoutY="159.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="A standard Scrabble board will consist of cells that are located in a large square grid. The board offers 15 cells high and 15 cells wide. The tiles used on the game will fit in each cell on the board." wrappingWidth="647.89453125">
