      <Text fill="WHITE" fontSmoothingType="LCD" layoutX="472.0" layoutY="411.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Every player will start their turn by drawing seven tiles from the Scrabble bag. There are three options during any turn. The player can place a word, they can exchange tiles for new tiles or they can choose to pass. In most cases, players will try to place a word as the other two options will result in no score." wrappingWidth="647.8945312499999">
         <font>
            <Font name="System Italic" size="18.0" />
         </font></Text>
