      <Text fill="WHITE" fontSmoothingType="LCD" layoutX="472.0" layoutY="628.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Once all tiles are gone from the bag and a single player has placed all of their tiles, the game will end and the player with the highest score wins." wrappingWidth="647.89453125">
